{"id": "1493120931927687218", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Desc:\n> 队伍唯一：主动切换触腕姿态、使用猩红熔炉、释放「湮灭」后，抽 1 张装备者的指令卡，每个效果各 3 回合冷却。完成探索后，所有唤醒体获得的同调率提高 <WeaponEffect_Num:[StateArg1]%>。\n\n> After switching Tentacle Stances, using Crimson Furnace, or unleashing \"Annihilation,\" draw the wielder's Command Card ×1; each effect has a cooldown of 3 turns. After the Exploration, all Awakeners in the team gain +<WeaponEffect_Num:[StateArg1]%> Affinity.\n\nWeaponDesc:\n> 主动切换触腕姿态(当前剩余 [DescArg1] 回合冷却)、使用猩红熔炉(当前剩余 [DescArg2] 回合冷却)、释放「湮灭」后(当前剩余 [DescArg3] 回合冷却)，抽 1 张装备者的指令卡，每个效果各 3 回合冷却。完成探索后，所有唤醒体获得的同调率提高 <WeaponEffect_Num:[StateArg1]%>。\n\n> After switching Tentacle Stances, using Crimson Furnace, or unleashing \"Annihilation,\" draw the wielder's Command Card ×1; each effect has a cooldown of 3 turns. After the Exploration, all Awakeners in the team gain +<WeaponEffect_Num:[StateArg1]%> Affinity.\n\nAm I correct to assume that [DescArg1], [DescArg2], and [DescArg3] in WeaponDesc here are cooldown timers?\nCan someone help me determine what format to write these into in EN?", "timestamp": "2026-04-13T05:29:31.017000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
